{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/M_shieldmaster_600x338.gif?t=1673444229\" /><br><strong>GLADIUM</strong> is an action game set in the Roman gladiatorial era. With a focus on brutal boss fights and a progression system based on blood and gold, you will have to embrace death to be victorious.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">HEART POUNDING BOSS FIGHTS</h2>Challenge the unforgiving champions of the arena with their own unique mechanics and tactics!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ACTION COMBAT</h2>Fast-paced action combat featuring dodging, parrying, special attacks and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GLADIATORS OF OLD</h2>Fight against enemy gladiators with appearance and behaviour based on the gladiator classes of ancient Rome, from the Murmillo to the Crupellarius!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">PIT FIGHTING</h2>Get a random weapon and fight one versus one against another gladiator with his own random weapon!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENDLESS MODE</h2>Face never-ending waves of enemies and bosses with highscores. Display your blood-spilling ability with online leaderboards!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">UPGRADES AND UNLOCKS</h2>Earn coins in the arena to purchase new weapons and shields - find your playstyle! <br>Unlock unique helmets offering diverse effects from completing various tasks!<br>Spend blood to unlock and customize the powers of your special attack!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1118410/extras/M_sitting_600x168.gif?t=1673444229\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Aetius, The First Spear","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1118410/7292a2958487cd81b84d0da999a860fb6a8a5588.jpg"},{"name":"Quick Feet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1118410/fa1853e1c40c1168048f59319c6a721192d28020.jpg"},{"name":"Thaddeus, The Shield Of Carthage","path":"https://cdn.akama